        <abstract>
            <p>CD’s respect for JS’s indomitable work and interesting experiments increases steadily.</p> 
<p>His gratitude for the primulas and the astonishing <hi rend="italic">Gongora</hi> specimen.</p> 
            <p>Asks JS’s opinion about crossing a primrose with the pollen of a wild cowslip and of a cultivated polyanthus.</p>
